title: Dave's Old Porn (season 1 and 2) (HDTV)
description:
Dave's Old Porn is a comedy show starring Dave Attell that premiered on Showtime on October 20, 2011. Attell has described the series as "the Mystery Science Theater of porn."

Attell and his co-hosts review pornographic films from the genre's "golden age" of the 1970s and 1980s. Attell is joined by a fellow comedian to make jokes about a variety of porn clips. Typically, the pair view clips from movies of one particular porn star. Then, near the end of the episode, they are joined by the porn star whose movies they've been viewing over the course of the episode.

All sexual acts such as fellatio, cunnilingus, genitalia and ejaculations are censored, with either an image of a VHS cassette, cartoons, a strategically placed image of Attell's face, or the sofa the hosts are using.


These are complete HDTV rips of season 1 and 2.
